Summary: Unknown object apeared to flame out
divs: Sighting Detailsat 0318 hours above the air traffic control tower in SLC, Utah I observed an unknown object in the sky about 100 feet in the air the object was dark and not reflective the object was in the shape of a a dart pointy on the front but more rounded at the rear the object apeared to flameout as if turning of the after burner or turning out its flame before it flew over the city the object was flying from west to east after it flamed out I was only able to follow it for about two seconds until I lost track of it
